<p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">为筑牢校园安全防线，传递细致入微的关怀，保障每一位同学的住宿安全与生活质量。10月30日晚，经济管理学院党总支书记蔡平，学工办主任郭伟及全体辅导员深入学生宿舍开展查寝工作。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>01 查寝动员</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174453947.png" alt="1762174453947.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174453947.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174540290.png" alt="1762174540290.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174540290.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">为确保查寝工作能以饱满的热情与严谨的态度顺利开展，经济管理学院提前召开查寝动员大会。会议强调查寝人员在认真排查住宿隐患、规范住宿秩序的同时也应向学子传递关怀温度。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>02 寝室检查</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">在查寝过程中，辅导员们秉持着“安全第一”原则，细致排查大功率电器、私拉电线、消防通道堵塞等隐患，不遗漏任何细节；同时也带着耐心与同理心沟通，倾听同学需求、解答疑问，传递来自学院的关心与重视。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174582092.png" alt="1762174582092.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174582092.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174609208.png" alt="1762174609208.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174609208.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174625281.png" alt="1762174625281.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174625281.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174636814.png" alt="1762174636814.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174636814.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174670947.png" alt="1762174670947.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174670947.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174682758.png" alt="1762174682758.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174682758.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174737778.png" alt="1762174737778.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174737778.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>03 结语</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174800291.png" alt="1762174800291.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762174800291.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">宿舍安全无小事，平安相伴是初心。让我们携手同行，把宿舍打造成安全、舒适、温馨的港湾，在安心的环境中逐梦成长，共赴青春美好时光！</span></p>